The internship followed a structured, phased methodology aligned with standard software development lifecycle principles while accommodating the constraints of a hybrid work environment. The approach commenced with comprehensive analysis of the existing website architecture and corporate branding guidelines during initial on-site engagement. Requirements gathering sessions established clear functional and aesthetic parameters, emphasizing minimalism, loading speed optimization, and navigation simplicity.

