### 6.3 UI Testing
User Interface testing ensured visual consistency and aesthetic compliance with client minimalism requirements. Venkateshwaran conducted pixel-perfect comparisons between implemented pages and design specifications, verifying color accuracy using digital color meter tools to confirm hex code adherence to branding guidelines (#003366 for primary blue, #FFFFFF for backgrounds, #333333 for text). Typography testing confirmed font family consistency, size hierarchies (H1: 2.5rem, H2: 2rem, body: 1rem), and line spacing (1.5-1.6 for body text) across all pages.

