Resolution required aggressive CSS refactoring to establish unified styling hierarchies, standardization of HTML structural templates ensuring consistent `<main>` content wrapping, and systematic removal of inline styles that had proliferated during rapid development phases. Integration testing protocols identified and resolved these conflicts through iterative merging and cross-page navigation verification.

